Definition: the function of pointing or specifying from the perspective of a participant in an act of speech or writing
Example: aspects of a communication whose interpretation depends on knowledge of the context in which the communication occurs
Synonyms: adj, pert, deictic, semantics, the, function, of, pointing, or, specifying, from, perspective, a, participant, in, an, act, speech, writing, aspects, communication, whose, interpretation, depends, on, knowledge, context, which, occurs
Category: noun.cognition
